CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 27, 1957, pg. A3 reads: "Frogs Week Committee - These five men are the committee in charge of the annual Frogs Week festivities which will get under way Sunday. Seated, left to right at Loendi Club are Wendell Freeland, Henry R. Smith and William Frederick.  Standing: Linn Washington and Robert M. Ratcliffe.  Mr. Ratcliffe and Mr. Freeland are co-chairman of Frogs Week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: FROGS members, seated from left: Wendell Freeland, Henry R. Smith, and William Frederick; standing: Linn Washington and Robert M. Ratcliffe, gathered in Loendi Club
